These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, soul, pop, folk, house, indie
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of house##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of indie##1
6. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Music-Genre      | soul  | indie | house | salsa | folk | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
There are 6 different nationalities: russian, turkish, dutch, brazilian, colombian, egyptian
1. the brazilian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the russian is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the dutch is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
6. the turkish is on the right of the dutch##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the egyptian##1
8. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| Nationality           | dutch | turkish    | russian      | egyptian  | brazilian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
6 different games are played: bridge, chess, scrabble, domino, canasta, whist
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
8. the person playing scrabble is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Game   | scrabble | whist | bridge | chess   | canasta | domino |

