.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, townhouse, cape-cod, art-deco, ranch-style
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, helicopter, ship, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the cape-cod house##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
7. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| House   | townhouse  | cape-cod | farmhouse      | gothic-revival  | ranch-style | art-deco |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi  | snowmobile | helicopter | ship  | bike    |

