4. the australian is on the left of the townhouse house##1
5. the german is the farmhouse house##1
6. the palace house is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the tower house is on the left of the palace house##1
9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| House   | farmhouse    | art-deco    | townhouse | tower     | palace   | colonial     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

