8. the person who likes pink is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | reggae     | hip-hop    | funk  | punk          |
| Color         | ebony  | yellow | brown | fuchsia | blood-red | pink |

