.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, havana, cain, blend, alhambra, baccarat
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the van is the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Cigar    | alhambra | havana | blend | baccarat    | tiparillo | cain      |
| Transport   | ship   | bike     | bus      | subway | van           | snowmobile |

