.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, fuchsia, ivory, turquise, lavender, yellow
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who likes black##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
9. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Color   | fuchsia   | black | yellow | lavender | ivory | turquise |

