.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: electronic, d&b, reggae, funk, house, hip-hop
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the coach is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of house##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the fan of electronic is the manager##1
8. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | electronic     | reggae | d&b | funk | house   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

