.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-16::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles, reading, rock-climbing
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, dahlia, zinnia, azalea, daisy
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | fishing  | rock-climbing | puzzles       | hiking   |
| Flower   | dahlia | balloon-flower     | iris | azalea        | zinnia | daisy |

